public class XMPPEventExtension
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.jivesoftware.smack.packet.PacketExtension, MonitoringEvent

XMPP/Jabber extention for Avalanche Events. Implements standard Avalanche MonitoringEvent interface so it can be used with xmpp/jabber without changing rest of Avalanche system.
